quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  7,88,"Nnan d imvebbĂŽen imzuxiyen, n ugdud is,: \"a k nessuffe$ a CuĂąayeb, keĂ§Ă§, akked wid iumnen yidek, si temdint nne$, ne$ a d tu$alev ar ddin nne$\". Inna: \"xas nugi"
  7,89,"Ihi, nger ed tikerkas $ef Ăebbi, ma nu$al ar ddin nnwen, mbaĂąd ma Isellek a$ Ăebbi, segs. Ur a$ ilaq ara a nu$al $uĂŽes, siwa ma Irad Ăebbi, Mass nne$. Mass nne$ IssemĂȘalleq i yal cci s tmusni. Nepkel $ef Ăebbi\". A Mass nne$! Fru p garane$ akked ugdud nne$, s tidep. KeĂ§Ă§ Tifev akw wid iferrun"
  7,90,"Nnan imvebbĂŽen, wid ijehlen, n ugdud is: \"ma teddam d CuĂąayeb, war ccekk a pxesĂŽem"
  7,91,"Tewwet iten zzenzla, gwran d, deg ixxamen nnsen, d loeppat"
  7,92,"Wid iskaddben CuĂąayeb, u$alen amzun ur zdi$en. Wid iskaddben CuĂąayeb, d nitni ay d imexĂ»uĂŽen"
  7,93,"IwexxeĂŽ asen, u inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ni$ ssawve$ awen d tibĂŽatin n Mass iw, neĂ»ĂȘe$ kwen. Amek ara $weble$ $ef ugdud ijehliyen"
  7,94,"Ur Nuzen ara nnbi ar temdint, mebla ma Newwet imezda$ is s cedda, akked lemveĂŽĂŽa, amar ad ĂȘiwten"
  7,95,"Sinna, Nerra ise$ deg umkan n tucmip, armi wexxĂŽen, nnan: \"ni$ jeĂŽĂŽben imezwura nne$ lemveĂŽĂŽa akked ttrika\". Newwet iten deqzalla, nitni ur bnin"
  7,96,"Lemmer kan uminen u ĂȘezzben imezda$ n temdinin, war ccekk, ad asen Nelli lbaĂŽakat seg igenni akked tmurt. Maca, skaddben. NessemĂȘalleq asen, ilmend n wayen keppben"
  7,97,"Day $ilen imezda$ n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nneÂŁ, deg yiv, nitni ĂźĂźsen"
  7,98,"Ne$ day $ilen imezda$ n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nneÂŁ, deg wazal, nitni ppuraren"
  7,99,"Day $ilen sellken i tandit n Ăebbi? Siwa agdud i ixesĂŽen, i i$ilen sellken i tandit n Ăebbi"
  7,100,"Ne$ day ur d Iban ara, i wid ara iweĂŽten tamurt, deffir imezda$ is, ar, ma ihwa yaÂŁ, a ten Newwet $ef ibekkaven nnsen, a Nesle$ ulawen nnsen, d$a nitni ur sellen"
  7,101,"D timdinin agi, i$ef ak NĂȘekku, si teqĂ»ivin nnsent. Ni$ usan $uĂŽsent imazanen nnsent, s ubeggen. Ur llint d tid ara iamnen deg wayen skaddbent uqbel. Akka i Iselle$ Ăebbi ulawen ijehliyen"
  7,102,"Ur Nufi nnesba ar tegwti nnsen. Nufa, tegwti nnsen, d iballa$en"
  7,103,"Sinna, deffir sen, Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nneÂŁ, ar FerĂąun akked imvebbĂŽen is. Densen ten. Wali amek tevĂŽa d ifessaden"
  7,104,"Inna Musa: \"a FerĂąun! Nek d amazan s$uĂŽ Mass imavalen"
  7,105,"D Ă»Ă»eĂȘ, ur qqaĂŽe$, $ef Ăebbi, siwa tidep. Ih, usi$ kwen id, s ubeggen n Mass nnwen. Ihi, azen yidi At IsĂŽail"
  7,106,"Inna: \"ma tusiv d s ussekni, zzi t id, ma tessawalav tidep"
  7,107,"IveggeĂŽ taĂąkwazt is, appan d azrem n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  7,108,"Issuffe$ ed afus is, iban ed d amellal i imnezhen"
  7,109,"Nnan d imvebbĂŽen n ugdud n FerĂąun: \"wagi, s tidep, d aseĂȘĂȘar amusnaw"
  7,110,"Ib$a a kwen issuffe$ si tmurt nnwen, d acu t lameĂŽ nnwen"
  7,111,"Nnan: \"anef as, neppa akked gma s. Azen iberraĂȘen ar temdinin"
  7,112,ad ak d awin yal aseĂȘĂȘar amusnaw
  7,113,"Usan d iseĂȘĂȘaren n FerĂąun, nnan: \"s tidep, ad a$ tkafiv, ma d nekwni ara i$elben"
  7,114,"Inna: \"ih, u, s tidep, a ppilim d iqĂŽiben"
  7,115,"Nnan: \"a Musa! A pveggĂŽev keĂ§Ă§, ne$ a nveggeĂŽ nekwni"
  7,116,"Inna: \"veggĂŽet\"! Mi veggĂŽen, sdehcen allen n l$aci, ssagwden ten. Bbwin d ssĂȘur anect ilat"